content.html:
please can people not share pirate links to Mira's zine.

It's just $10.
http://fuckingtranswomen.org/

It was her pride of work, she was working on a sequel and together we had another written project that was 90% finished for a first chapter in a series.

The money goes to the bellwether family as we figure out things like funeral arrangements, medical bills and all the extras.
